Package org.example

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataStreamHandle
    DataStreamHandle class is responsible for requesting data from the Alpha Vantage API, processing the data, calling the Median Selection class to obtain the relevant median, and then processing the data into the format required by JFreeChart.
    DrawChart
    Draw and display a time series chart
    HeapPriorityQueue
    An implementation of a priority queue using a list-based heap.
    Main
    The Main class is responsible for running the program and generating a stock price chart.
    MedianSelection
    Compute the median of a stream of Double
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DataStreamHandle.Interval
    Time interval between two consecutive data points in the time series
    DataStreamHandle.OutputSize
    The data size of API call
